Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.64,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}あの白い鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.42,0:22:46.75,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}翔ける　大空で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:51.83,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}誰かに呼ばれたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}大丈夫さ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.95,0:23:06.80,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}大事なことはこの胸にある
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:10.66,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}思いがすべて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.96,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}今だけが　今
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.96,0:23:22.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}花の名前を集めるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.95,0:23:28.59,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}大切なもの増えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.59,0:23:32.25,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}微睡んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.25,0:23:41.90,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}夢も傷も　連れて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.51,0:22:34.77,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}拂晓前的一场梦
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.64,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}那只白鸟
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.42,0:22:46.75,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在天空中翱翔
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.75,0:22:51.83,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}天际间有谁在呼唤着我
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.83,0:22:57.95,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}不用担心
Dialogue: 1,0:22:57.95,0:23:06.80,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}要事我始终铭记
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.80,0:23:10.66,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}万千思绪
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.66,0:23:15.96,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}此时涌上心头
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.96,0:23:22.95,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}珍视之物一件件增加
